page.title: 04Mi Setdiz.
page.content: {Yorkshire dialect's}almooast a {langwij}on its ooan,an it's spok in{Gret Ohtun.}A gerrup abart ayfe seven on Setdiz.When a gerrup a gu intut bathrooam an a gerra wesh,an a brush me teeth.A run darnstairs an a switch on't telly. A gu intert kichin an a getmi clooarz.A bring 'em intat' room an a get drest.A pu'teletext on ter see what's ont'telly .Yousjerly thuz a cartoon on at ayfe nine follerd at twenny ter ten by Scooby Doo, which is reight good{entertainment}.When av lukt at what's on,a switch tele off an a tek sum munny art me mam's purse.A oppen't dooar an a gu in tut shed an a get mi bike. A ride tut shop an a by ar paper an a tek it up t'ar 'owse. A gu in an a purrit on mi dads armchair an a gu back art aggeean. A lake on mi bike wi mi mates til mi mam sharts mi in fommi snap.Eeh a dunafe luv{Setdiz!
